description: The SXSW AI House is a two-day immersive experience showcasing Austin’s booming AI ecosystem. Step into a curated space where top AI startups bring their tech to life with hands-on demos, deep-dive conversations, and connection. Expect live panels, interactive showcases, and great food—all designed to spark ideas and collaborations. Come see the future of AI, Austin-style.

name: Marketing Leaders Brunch
description: The Marketer's Brunch: Conversations & Strategy, an exclusive invite-only event as part of Lumos House event series, bringing together top marketing leaders, CMOs, and strategists for a catered brunch at a luxe Austin property during SXSW 2025.

name: Frontiers of Innovation Day in Austin TX (SXSW 2025) | Presented by the Frontier Collective
description: Frontiers of Innovation Day at SXSW 2025 is a full-day event featuring discussions, demos, and networking opportunities with industry leaders in AI, computing, EV, climate-tech, and more.

name: TXHQ: Australia Downtown Rooftop Event (Save-the-Date)
description: TXHQ: Australia Downtown Rooftop Event is a networking event showcasing Australia's tech innovation, government initiatives, and mining/agriculture tech. The event includes a trade relationship discussion, venture panel, happy hour, and more.

name: Publishers and Journalists in the Fediverse
description: Join Flipboard + Surf and Marci McCue for a series of discussions and panels on publishing, journalism, and audience engagement.

name: Crowdstake @ SXSW 2025
description: Join the Blockchain Crowdfunding for Film & Games event at Mort Subite Belgian Beer Bar during SXSW 2025. This event is designed to unite film producers, game developers, and blockchain enthusiasts. Enjoy complimentary Spanish Tapas, beer, wine, cider, and bubbly water while networking.

name: LTX Studio: Austin Workshop & Mixer at Hotel Magdalena
description: LTX Studio: Austin Workshop & Mixer at Hotel Magdalena is an immersive workshop for creative agencies, marketers, and entertainment professionals to learn about LTX Studio, an AI-driven filmmaking platform. The event includes real-world examples and hands-on experience with the platform, as well as gourmet appetizers.

name: SXSW XR Mixer: VR, AR, XR Meetup
description: Join us for the SXSW XR Mixer, an exclusive AR/VR/XR meetup put on by ATXR and hosted at Viewer Ready! Austin’s tech scene is booming, and this event is all about bringing together innovators, creators, and industry professionals from both inside and outside the city for SXSW. With drinks, snacks, and hands-on tech demos, we’re creating a space for networking, collaboration, and showcasing cutting-edge projects.

name: 404 Takeover and Party
description: 404 Takeover and Party hosted by Flipboard + Surf, featuring discussions on AI and independent media, followed by an afterparty sponsored by DeleteMe.

name: The Untold Story of Spin with Euwyn Poon (Founder, Spin)
description: An invite-only event series for the most visionary founders, builders, and leaders in media & tech. Powered by Blindspot and Andrew Yeung, set in an exclusive mansion—free to attend. A curated list of notable technology founders, investors, and leaders in media and entertainment will discuss the transformation of urban mobility and scaling a startup.

name: GP&LP FAMILY OFFICES 🌟 MICHELIN STAR 🌟 DINNER & SXSW KICKOFF
description: SXSW 2025 KICK OFF​🌟 MICHELIN STAR 🌟 ​GP&LP FAMILY OFFICES DINNER 2025 MARCH​INVITE ONLY!​VC/PE GROUPS & ENTREPRENEUR.VC would like to invite you to a small private curated group of GP&LP.  ​Get to know each other, share best practices, deal flow and trade war stories.  ​APPROVAL will be done by the planning committee.  ​LIMITED SEATS!  ​INVITES NON-TRANSFERABLE. ​ NO + 1s​PLEASE, RSVP ASAP!  ​LOVE ❤️ TO SEE 😍 U!

name: Topgolf Tech Mixer with BairesDev
description: Join us for an exclusive Topgolf Tech Mixer with BairesDev—a premier networking event designed for tech leaders looking to connect during #SXSW. Enjoy great company, casual conversations, and a little friendly competition—all in a relaxed and engaging environment. Spots are limited—RSVP today!

name: Founders Run & Coffee! (SXSW Edition)
description: Join Founders Common for an early morning run with other founders, operators & creatives at SXSW! Come run and then hang out afterward to chat with new friends across the startup community over coffee.

name: Responsible AI Investors - SXSW
description: Polygraf AI is hosting an exclusive and invitation-only event at SXSW for investors to discuss Responsible AI and AI in Defense. This event is focused on AI Ethics, Deepfakes, and AI/Data Governance, and will bring together top investors, academics, and industry professionals in the AI ecosystem.

name: TEXAS EMBASSY: Texas Innovation Ecosystem
description: Join the 1st annual Texas Innovation Ecosystem event at the Texas Embassy, showcasing the latest innovations in Texas tech entrepreneurship, investing, and updates.

name: AI for Women
description: Join us for an exclusive morning of panels, networking, and brunch, where we explore how AI is reshaping the women's health landscape. This event is designed for founders, investors, industry leaders, and professionals in the women’s health space who are interested in how AI can improve health outcomes and drive innovation.

name: UKHOUSE @ SXSW - The Future of AI: Who wins, who loses and how do we shape it?
description: Join us at UK House for a deep dive panel exploring money and power in the world of AI. Our panel will debate whether current AI investments amount to a bubble or are the tip of an iceberg and debate which countries are making the smartest AI plays. This is not just a question about money, it is also about power – who gets to shape the future of AI– governments, tech giants or entirely new players?

name: Entertainment, Music, & Media Brunch
description: The Lumos House Entertainment, Music, & Media Brunch is an invite-only event series that brings together top executives from record labels, management firms, & agencies for a morning of food and connection. Hosted in an exclusive mansion in Austin, Texas during SXSW 2025, this event promises to spark engaging conversations among notable technology founders, investors, and leaders in media and entertainment.

name: Mionetto Salone
description: Experience The Italian Orange Soul with Mionetto! Enjoy art, music, cuisine, spritzes, and Prosecco to soak in the essence of Italy in Austin. Special programming includes live drawing, photography discussion, live music sessions, and DJ night.

name: WE ARE ARISING GREEN CARPET EVENT
description: We Are Arising Green Carpet Event is a transformative gathering during SXSW 2025 showcasing music, art, workshops, networking, and conscious solutions for a sustainable future. The event features workshops, panels, a concert, and opportunities to connect with thought leaders and change-makers.

name: GLEAN'S SXSW AI OPEN HOUSE
description: Join Glean at Electric Shuffle during SXSW for a casual AI Open House event featuring live demos and networking opportunities.

name: Authenticity Is Currency - How to Build a Brand People Genuinely Want to Follow
description: An invite-only event series for the most visionary founders, builders, and leaders in media & tech. Powered by Blindspot and Andrew Yeung, set in an exclusive mansion—free to attend.

name: 7BC Global VC Demo Day & VC Fund of Funds launch announcement & Austin Boomtown VC Insight Panel
description: 7BC Global VC Demo Day & VC Fund of Funds launch announcement & Austin Boomtown VC Insight Panel hosted by 7BC Venture Capital, Andrew Romans & Mehron Sharq. Celebrate the launch of the Global VC Demo Day event circuit and 7BC Capital. Networking reception exclusively for VCs and LPs. Serve drinks, bites, and free copies of Andrew Romans' latest books.

name: SXSW Rooftop Tech Mixer
description: Join us for a private SXSW Rooftop Tech Mixer hosted by Entre and Fidelity. Enjoy an open bar and good vibes with top tier founders and investors at a special rooftop location in downtown Austin. Entre is a professional network helping individuals and companies connect through events, content, and community. Fidelity Private Shares is committed to supporting the startup & venture capital community. Engine is a free travel platform for booking and managing work trips. Genius Wallet is the easiest way to buy meme coins and invest in crypto. TSIB specializes in risk management and insurance consulting for private equity firms, venture capitalists, high-growth startups, and other industries. WeWork provides flexible workspaces for individuals and companies. Rho is a banking platform offering corporate cards, banking, treasury, expense management, and more.

name: SXSW She Means Business: Ask Her Anything Hot Seat
description: Connecting female investors with founders, fostering collaborations between startups and advisors, & uniting women angel investors with other investing and VC professionals. Top investors from $100M+ funds and founders who’ve raised over $400M in the hot seat to answer burning questions. No scripts, no filters, just real talk on raising capital, scaling, and thriving as a woman in business. Expect bold conversations, high-impact networking, and a room full of women who get it.

name: NachoTuesday: SaaS & AI Founder + Investor Happy Hour
description: NachoTuesday: SaaS & AI Founder + Investor Happy Hour hosted by NachoNacho, Hubspot, LendFlow, Deel, Koop AI, and Skrillo. Exclusive event for SaaS & AI Founders, C-Suites, investors, tech media, and tech leaders.

name: Bo$$ Bites Austin (During SXSW)
description: Boss Bites is an exclusive event for venture-backed founders and investors in Austin during SXSW. It features panels with local startup and investor all-stars, followed by a VIP dinner where attendees switch seats to meet new people. Limited to 30 seats and attendees must apply to join.

name: Datasent VIP Lounge: Founders & Investors Cocktail Hour
description: Join Datasent for an intimate, invite-only cocktail hour during SXSW, bringing together top founders, investors, and industry leaders shaping the future of AI, privacy, and data-driven innovation. This exclusive gathering is designed for high-caliber networking over curated cocktails and delicious bites, fostering candid conversations and meaningful connections with Austin's most exclusive entrepreneurship community.

name: The Future of Middleware: Bridging the Gap to Modernization
description: Join us for an exclusive evening of thought-provoking conversation and networking focused on the transformative role of middleware in today’s technology landscape. This event is designed for investors and technology operators looking to deepen their understanding of middleware’s impact on scaling applications, driving innovation, and enabling transformation across industries.

name: AI Night ATX ~ w/ Cloudflare, GitHub, ElevenLabs & Jam.dev
description: AI Night ATX event featuring AI demos at Cloudflare's Austin HQ, with food, drinks, and networking opportunities. Hosted by Cloudflare, GitHub, ElevenLabs, and Jam.dev.

name: Batter Up! Austin
description: Batter Up! is a live pitch event for founders hosted by Hustle Fund, where founders can pitch their companies to investors and receive feedback. It's an in-person event with no virtual option, and the winner takes home a prize. The event includes networking opportunities, investor panels, and pizza for attendees.

name: Berlin Flat — Austin Edition
description: Berlin Flat returns to Austin, bringing together global minds for innovation, creativity, and connections. From startups to creatives, this event fosters collaboration and partnership-building.

name: Austin Digital Social Networking Mixer During SXSW
description: The Digital Social Hour Podcast event hosted by Sean Kelly during SXSW in Austin, Texas, bringing together influential individuals for networking, idea sharing, and partnerships.

name: 3rd Annual Context Ventures & Scout Ventures Happy Hour
description: The 3rd Annual Context Ventures & Scout Ventures Happy Hour hosted by Tim Hsia at Zilker Brewing Co. to discuss startups, defense tech, dual use, & military veteran topics. Sponsored by Perkins Coie.

name: Beyond Productivity: AI and the Future of Work
description: Join Glean, Codeium, and WWT for an exclusive evening at Electric Shuffle in Austin at SXSW, where industry leaders will explore the next phase of Agentic AI—moving beyond productivity to true intelligence and automation. Enjoy an evening of insightful discussion, networking, and interactive experiences with top AI innovators.

name: SXSW AI & Innovation VIP Forum
description: Join an exclusive, invitation-only evening of world-class networking, Argentine asado, and curated wine tasting in the heart of Austin during SXSW. Hosted by the Austin AI Lab, this gathering brings together top executives, technologists, and entrepreneurs for meaningful conversations in an intimate setting.

name: The Ace Exchange
description: The Ace Exchange is an invite-only poker night for top founders, investors, creators, and tech leaders, part of the Lumos House event series. The event offers high-stakes poker games and networking opportunities with curated technology leaders.

name: The Cometa Supper Club: SXSW 2025 Edition
description: Join us for yet another Cometa Supper Club Dinner hosted at SXSW 2025! Meet Cometa Community Members, learn about the work and passions of our Partners, and explore the buzz around Austin and SXSW!

name: Presented by Michigan: JMSN at SXSW
description: Michigan presents Detroit-raised alt-R&B icon, JMSN. An influential figure in the contemporary soul and alternative music scenes, the sought-after performer and producer brings his unforgettable stage presence to longtime fans and new converts at Michigan Day at SXSW. Join us, not only for a captivating performance with a special opening set from artist, Stoop Lee, but also an immersive experience that highlights Michigan’s thriving creator economy and bold innovation. Connect with visionary entrepreneurs, artists, and leaders shaping the future of creativity in Michigan. Come experience why You Can in Michigan—where originality thrives, and big ideas come to life.

name: The International House
description: Join us for the highly anticipated return of the International House, hosted by IA during SXSW! This annual event has become a cornerstone of innovation and global entrepreneurship, bringing together founders, investors, and industry leaders from across the world!
location: Austin Central Library, Austin Public Library

name: Private SXSW Launch: Authentic Texas BBQ Experience for Investors, Founders, and Product Leaders
description: Private event offering an authentic Texas BBQ experience for investors, founders, and product leaders during SXSW. Event includes luxurious transport, exclusive networking, top-tier BBQ, and historic ambiance.

name: International Pitch Competition @ The International House 2025
description: International Pitch Competition at The International House for international or foreign-born founders to showcase their startups and compete for a $500 cash prize
location: Austin Central Library, Austin Public Library

name: Resilient and Rising: The State and Future of Inclusion for US in Tech
description: Join Atlassian and Techqueria for a networking event aimed at driving technology innovation with Latine talent. Mix and mingle with industry leaders and tech enthusiasts at the Atlassian Austin office.

name: Climate Round Up: Innovation Showcase 2025
description: Annual innovation showcase for climate tech startups, investors, and leaders to connect and learn about the latest trends and developments in the field. The event will feature startup pitches, panel discussions, product showcases, and networking opportunities with food and beverages provided.

name: ATX Podcast Superfans MeetUp
description: Join the Austin game-changers, big thinkers, and podcast super fans for a high-energy meetup filled with next-level conversations and unexpected connections.

name: Elevate & Unwind Happy Hour
description: Join Panoplai & GoFasti for a happy hour event at Fogo De Chao - Austin during SXSW. Enjoy open bar, complimentary hors d’oeuvres, and networking with industry professionals in the AI and tech space.

name: Casting Call: Founder’s Feud at The International House 2025
description: Founder’s Feud is a high-energy, startup-themed game show where startup founders compete live on stage showcasing their knowledge of entrepreneurship, fundraising, and startup culture. It is an exclusive event open only to startup founders who are ready to bring their A-game.
location: Austin Central Library, Austin Public Library

name: 『MELT』150+ Founders x Investors Dynamic Network for SXSW
description: Highly-selective founders and investors network at SXSW with around 150 top-tier founders, VCs, and angel investors. Exclusive 2-hour networking session sponsored by cyber•Fund.

name: BEYOND THE BLOCK ATX
description: Third Planet Studio Presents: Beyond The Block Tour ATX during SXSW 2025 featuring live performances from Web3 artists, rising stars, and local talent. The event offers networking opportunities and a cutting-edge experience for music and Web3 enthusiasts.

name: SXSW AI HOUSE PARTY with Glean & Codeium
description: Join Glean & Codeium for an official SXSW party at Electric Shuffle in Downtown Austin! Enjoy an evening of cocktails, conversation, and cutting-edge AI insights. Registering does NOT guarantee entry; it will be first come, first serve while capacity allows. You must have your SXSW badge to attend.

name: Duetti Party in Austin
description: Duetti Party at Devil May Care in Austin with free drinks and DJ sets

name: The International House After Dark
description: The International House After Dark is a vibrant nightclub and dance party hosted by International Accelerator. Attendees can expect a live DJ, finger food & crafted cocktails, and exclusive networking with global innovators. It is an after-party aimed at unwinding, celebrating, and connecting in an electrifying atmosphere.
location: Austin Central Library, Austin Public Library

name: 8th Annual SXSW LATINAPALOOZA   featuring Patricia Vonne  No Badges Required          21+ FREE DAY SHOW!!!
description: The 8th Annual SXSW LATINAPALOOZA featuring Patricia Vonne is a showcase of Latina musical artists curated by Patricia Vonne. The event is open to all and features performances by various Latina performers representing diverse genres.

name: Amplitude x Braze Austin Meetup - SXSW
description: Amplitude x Braze Austin Meetup at RichesArt Gallery featuring legendary barbecue from La Barbecue, non-alcoholic drinks, and a live DJ. Connect with the community, share insights, and take a break from SXSW hustle.

name: SXSW Austin Crypto Social
description: Join us for the SXSW Austin Crypto Social Meetup: Unite & Network! This is the perfect afternoon for crypto enthusiasts to connect from 4 PM to 7 PM. Grab a drink and hang out with fellow geeks in one of Austin's great outdoor bars. Expect a laid-back atmosphere where you can meet new people, share ideas, and have some solid conversations. Location to be announced—stay tuned!

name: Austin DeoVR Networking Meet-Up
description: VR Creators Networking Event hosted by Nathalie & Karolina Báez featuring presentations on DeoVR and connecting VR enthusiasts, developers, and creators in person.

name: Austin Eclipse Festival- Portal To A New World
description: Austin Eclipse Festival- Portal To a New World is a part of the week-long conference, RegenWorld’25, during SXSW. The event includes music, networking, ceremony, dancing, and a live viewing of a Blood Moon Total Lunar Eclipse accompanied by an immersive soundscape experience.

name: Your Startup Sucks (SWSW) Pitch Comedy Show
description: Austin’s premier live pitch startup comedy show is back with Tequila 512! Watch brave and passionate founders pitch their (your) startups to a panel of seasoned VCs, and former founders for recognition and brutally honest (and hilarious) feedback. Enjoy open bar, mix and mingle before the show starts at 7:30 sharp.

name: Investors & Startups Reception x SXSW 2025
description: This high-caliber gathering will bring together top investors, CEOs of promising tech startups, and media leaders at the forefront of Water, Ocean, Blockchain, Deep Tech, AI, VR/AR, and Smart Cities. Engage with the brightest minds shaping the future of innovation and explore the transformative potential of these industries.

name: Future of Fashion at SXSW: Where Fashion, Tech, and Community Intersect
description: Join us for an immersive experience blending fashion, technology, and community at the Future of Fashion event hosted by REFIND at SXSW 2025. Explore the forefront of fashion through digital innovation and creative collaboration. Engage in insightful panels, interactive activations, demos, and networking opportunities. Experience a high-energy fashion show featuring visionary collections and a live musical performance.

name: [SXSW] - Degens - Cinema Projection 🍿
description: Join us for a private screening of the first scenes of 'Degens' : a feature film on the crypto ecosystem. Think HBO's 'Silicon Valley'—cringe humor mixed with storytelling and inside jokes from the crypto industry. Be the first to watch the first scenes of the show and discover bonuses and behind the scenes. The screening is followed by a Q&A session with Eliott Mogenet, writer and director. Registration is subject to approval by the host.

name: 🥣⚡🧇  Official Unofficial SatoshiO's xSW Breakfast Party
description: Official Unofficial SatoshiO's xSW Breakfast Party featuring healthy cereal, waffles, chicken and waffles, discussions on using Bitcoin in business, art, and wellness activities. Early Bird Discount available for tickets paid with Lightning or Bitcoin. Event is for individuals interested in health, Bitcoin, and business applications of cryptocurrency.

name: #ReverseSugarDaddy
description: Join Larry Chiang for the #ReverseSugarDaddy event at Fairmont Spa Austin during SXSW where they explore the concept of Gender reversal, VC exercises, paying seasoned executives as reverse sugar daddies, and empowering female entrepreneurs. Attendees will laugh, network, and learn about unique business models and party activations.

name: Startup Pitch & Networking in Austin
description: Startup Valley event focusing on driving innovation through startup events and networking in Austin, Texas. Participants can choose from different ticket types based on their preferences and engage with leading experts, founders, and investors in the Tech & Business industry. The event includes startup pitches, expert evaluations, networking opportunities, and access to a database of promising startups.
